{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01SF94hMcaNqKhocTALSA8Q8","type":"tool_result","content":"   300→\n   301→* prompt review stage\n   302→* validator voting/acceptance\n   303→* prompt replacement when approved\n   304→\n   305→### Validation profile execution\n   306→\n   307→**Value**\n   308→Applies different repo checks based on the type of work.\n   309→\n   310→**Owns behaviors**\n   311→\n   312→* `standard` validation profile\n   313→* `quick_dev` validation profile\n   314→* `docs_change` validation profile\n   315→* `ci_improvement` validation profile\n   316→* pre-commit and targeted repo checks\n   317→\n   318→### Requirements drafting\n   319→\n   320→**Value**\n   321→Produces implementation-ready requirements before project execution.\n   322→\n   323→**Owns behaviors**\n   324→\n   325→* staged requirements draft flow\n   326→* quick requirements draft flow\n   327→* question/answer cycles\n   328→* validation reports\n   329→* resume/cache\n   330→\n   331→### Project bootstrapping from requirements\n   332→\n   333→**Value**\n   334→Lets approved requirements become executable projects cleanly.\n   335→\n   336→**Owns behaviors**\n   337→\n   338→* project creation from requirements output\n   339→* prompt/project handoff\n   340→* optional convenience workflow composition\n   341→\n   342→### Automation runtime\n   343→\n   344→**Value**\n   345→Turns issues, labels, and commands into orchestrated execution.\n   346→\n   347→**Owns behaviors**\n   348→\n   349→* daemon polling and dispatch\n   350→* label-based routing\n   351→* explicit command routing\n   352→* worktree leasing\n   353→* task lifecycle\n   354→* PR/watcher behavior\n   355→* rebase flows\n   356→\n   357→### Operator inspection and recovery surface\n   358→\n   359→**Value**\n   360→Makes the tool safe to operate.\n   361→\n   362→**Owns behaviors**\n   363→\n   364→* `run status`\n   365→* `run history`\n   366→* `run tail`\n   367→* `run