me cheap.\n  4189→\n  4190→* **Goal**\n  4191→\n  4192→  * implement `quick_dev`, `docs_change`, and `ci_improvement` on the same engine\n  4193→  * wire their validation profiles and final-review defaults\n  4194→\n  4195→* **Prerequisites**\n  4196→\n  4197→  * Slices 2, 6, 7, 8\n  4198→\n  4199→* **Exact scope**\n  4200→\n  4201→  * quick_dev preset\n  4202→  * docs_change preset\n  4203→  * ci_improvement preset\n  4204→  * preset-specific validation profiles\n  4205→  * preset-specific final-review policy\n  4206→\n  4207→* **Out-of-scope**\n  4208→\n  4209→  * user-defined workflows\n  4210→\n  4211→* **Files/modules likely affected**\n  4212→\n  4213→  * flow catalog\n  4214→  * validation profile registry\n  4215→  * stage library\n  4216→  * CLI project creation validation\n  4217→\n  4218→* **Ports/contracts introduced or changed**\n  4219→\n  4220→  * preset registry API\n  4221→  * validation profile registry API\n  4222→\n  4223→* **Scenarios covered**\n  4224→\n  4225→  * quick_dev shared engine\n  4226→  * docs validation flow\n  4227→  * CI validation flow\n  4228→  * final review disabled by preset\n  4229→\n  4230→* **Test strategy**\n  4231→\n  4232→  * preset transition tests\n  4233→  * validation profile tests\n  4234→  * conformance scenarios\n  4235→\n  4236→* **Migration strategy**\n  4237→\n  4238→  * preset catalog becomes operator-visible through `flow show`\n  4239→\n  4240→* **Rollback or safety considerations**\n  4241→\n  4242→  * avoid preset-specific fields in state model\n  4243→\n  4244→* **Risks**\n  4245→\n  4246→  * hiding preset-specific behavior in ad hoc hooks\n  4247→\n  4248→## Slice 10: Requirements Drafting and project handoff\n  4249→\n  4250→* **Slice name**\n  4251→  Requirements drafting and project seed handoff\n  4252→\n  4253→* **Bounded context**\n  4254→  Requirements Drafting + Workspace Governance + Project & Run Record\n  4255→\n  4256→* **Why it exists**\n  4257→  Requirements are a real product capability and should plug cleanly into the new architecture.\n  4258→\n  4259→* **Goal**\n  4260→\n  4261→  * implement staged requirements draft\n  4262→  * implement quick draft\n  4263→  * implement validation and cache\n  4264→  * hand off approved drafts into project creation\n  4265→\n  4266→* **Prerequisites**\n  4267→\n  4268→  * Slices 3-5 and basic project creation\n  4269→\n  4270→* **Exact scope**\n  4271→\n  4272→  * `requirements draft`\n  4273→  * `requirements quick`\n  4274→  * `requirements show`\n  4275→  * `requirements answer`\n  4276→  * project creation from requirements seed\n  4277→\n  4278→* **Out-of-scope**\n  4279→\n  4280→  * daemon interactive requirements routing\n  4281→\n  4282→* **Files/modules likely affected**\n  4283→\n  4284→  * `contexts/requirements_drafting/*`\n  4285→  * CLI requirements commands\n  4286→  * project creation handoff logic\n  4287→\n  4288→* **Ports/contracts introduced or changed**\n  4289→\n  4290→  * `RequirementsPort`\n  4291→  * project-seed DTOs\n  4292→\n  4293→* **Scenarios covered**\n  4294→\n  4295→  * staged draft run\n  4296→  * cached resume\n  4297→  * quick draft approval\n  4298→  * create project from requirements output\n  4299→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01TEaD8r9ay6pGSRWy6ah8ZA","session_id":"62aed473-a912-4db2-a48b-52d5c598eaf3","uuid":"c13aacf2-cae1-4ba3-913f-dd7f7441b234"}
